00:16:14,440 --> 00:16:15,759
I'm not here to complain.

285
00:16:16,559 --> 00:16:18,519
Director Lu, I discussed it
with you before

286
00:16:18,519 --> 00:16:20,120
and sought your consent, right?

287
00:16:24,320 --> 00:16:25,200
I told you.

288
00:16:25,919 --> 00:16:26,879
Sometimes,

289
00:16:27,399 --> 00:16:29,200
experiments are meant to disprove.

290
00:16:30,240 --> 00:16:31,879
Your experiment can only prove

291
00:16:31,879 --> 00:16:33,679
that Tu Huaiwei lied.

292
00:16:33,879 --> 00:16:35,480
It can't prove that he committed murder.

293
00:16:35,679 --> 00:16:36,759
My experiment can prove

294
00:16:36,759 --> 00:16:37,639
that the two kids

295
00:16:37,639 --> 00:16:39,360
were not shaken off the boat,

296
00:16:39,360 --> 00:16:40,679
but were pushed off.

297
00:16:40,879 --> 00:16:42,000
And the one who did that

298
00:16:42,000 --> 00:16:43,120
can only be Tu Huaiwei.

299
00:16:43,120 --> 00:16:45,279
If this doesn't count
as ruling out reasonable doubts,

300
00:16:45,279 --> 00:16:47,039
what does count?

301
00:16:47,039 --> 00:16:48,480
I am ruling out reasonable doubts.

302
00:16:57,159 --> 00:16:57,919
Lin,

303
00:16:59,240 --> 00:17:02,480
you asked me if eggs
can be used to make rice rolls,

304
00:17:02,720 --> 00:17:04,079
and I said yes.

305
00:17:04,960 --> 00:17:06,359
But now you're saying

306
00:17:06,359 --> 00:17:07,920
eggs are just rice rolls.

307
00:17:09,279 --> 00:17:10,200
Is this scientific?

308
00:17:15,000 --> 00:17:16,880
He acts like a ghost every day.

309
00:17:18,240 --> 00:17:18,848
I...

310
00:17:20,279 --> 00:17:21,160
We shall do it

311
00:17:22,039 --> 00:17:23,119
in a scientific way.

312
00:17:31,319 --> 00:17:32,640
Just look how stubborn he is.

313
00:17:32,799 --> 00:17:34,160
You two are equally matched.

314
00:17:34,319 --> 00:17:35,599
I am deeply convinced

315
00:17:35,599 --> 00:17:36,680
that it's Tu Huaiwei.

316
00:17:36,680 --> 00:17:38,000
Ma'am, it must be Tu Huaiwei.

317
00:17:38,000 --> 00:17:38,799
It's really him.

318
00:17:38,799 --> 00:17:39,519
You put yourself

319
00:17:39,519 --> 00:17:41,240
in the shoes of those two poor kids?

320
00:17:41,240 --> 00:17:42,279
I didn't.

321
00:17:44,519 --> 00:17:45,839
A person's subjective state

322
00:17:45,839 --> 00:17:47,640
is not about what he says,

323
00:17:47,640 --> 00:17:49,839
but is verified
through his objective behavior.

324
00:17:49,839 --> 00:17:52,759
- Okay, I admit...
- You're handling the case emotionally.

325
00:17:52,759 --> 00:17:54,000
I admit I'm angry.

326
00:17:54,119 --> 00:17:55,799
Tell me if you are angry.

327
00:17:55,920 --> 00:17:57,319
I didn't put myself in it.

328
00:17:57,880 --> 00:17:59,079
I simply believe

329
00:17:59,319 --> 00:18:01,079
Tu Huaiwei absolutely did it.

330
00:18:01,079 --> 00:18:01,599
And why?

331
00:18:01,599 --> 00:18:02,759
Xiaohua and Xiaohu could not

332
00:18:02,759 --> 00:18:03,839
have jumped on their own.

333
00:18:04,200 --> 00:18:05,720
They couldn't have unbuckled

334
00:18:05,720 --> 00:18:06,519
and jumped.

335
00:18:06,720 --> 00:18:08,359
They could only have been pushed by him.

336
00:18:08,359 --> 00:18:09,440
Otherwise, convince me.

337
00:18:09,440 --> 00:18:10,720
Is there any reasonable doubt?

338
00:18:11,319 --> 00:18:12,400
What else can be ruled out?

339
00:18:14,599 --> 00:18:15,440
Here, take a look.

340
00:18:15,440 --> 00:18:16,640
Do you remember this case?

341
00:18:18,160 --> 00:18:19,880
Wangjiang's Jane Doe case
five years ago.

342
00:18:19,880 --> 00:18:20,920
You were on this case.

343
00:18:21,440 --> 00:18:22,279
This case

344
00:18:22,279 --> 00:18:23,880
had confessions from the suspect

345
00:18:23,880 --> 00:18:25,079
and DNA evidence,

346
00:18:25,480 --> 00:18:27,160
but the victim's identity was unknown.

347
00:18:27,319 --> 00:18:29,160
The suspect withdrew the confession

348
00:18:29,400 --> 00:18:30,759
and evaded the murder charge.

349
00:18:31,640 --> 00:18:32,599
I didn't accept that.

350
00:18:32,599 --> 00:18:35,440
But we need to have
a complete chain of evidence.

351
00:18:36,160 --> 00:18:37,720
Director Lu is a technical expert.

352
00:18:37,728 --> 00:18:39,200
He only acknowledges evidence.

353
00:18:40,160 --> 00:18:43,039
He takes an objective view

354
00:18:43,039 --> 00:18:44,799
to oversee our rationality.

355
00:18:47,000 --> 00:18:47,559
He is slow

356
00:18:47,559 --> 00:18:48,319
at everything.

357
00:18:48,319 --> 00:18:49,400
He supervises slowly too.

358
00:18:49,799 --> 00:18:51,119
Because you never know

359
00:18:51,119 --> 00:18:52,359
what unbelievable things

360
00:18:52,359 --> 00:18:54,440
the defendant will say in court.

361
00:18:56,640 --> 00:18:57,720
Xiaohua woke up.

362
00:19:01,640 --> 00:19:02,559
Thank you.

363
00:19:13,039 --> 00:19:13,680
Hua,

364
00:19:14,400 --> 00:19:17,559
Dr. Sun and the nurse came to see you.

365
00:19:18,039 --> 00:19:20,000
Let them check you out, okay?

366
00:19:20,400 --> 00:19:21,839
Be good, Hua.

367
00:19:22,759 --> 00:19:25,599
If you think it's okay,

368
00:19:25,799 --> 00:19:28,759
open your little hands, okay?

369
00:19:30,640 --> 00:19:31,519
Hua, be good.

370
00:19:32,759 --> 00:19:33,279
Come on.

371
00:19:34,880 --> 00:19:36,640
Open your little hands.

372
00:19:50,400 --> 00:19:51,960
Let Dr. Sun

373
00:19:52,279 --> 00:19:55,680
give you a small checkup.

374
00:19:55,839 --> 00:19:56,640
Okay?

375
00:20:00,599 --> 00:20:01,480
Good girl.

376
00:20:07,552 --> 00:20:08,640
- Captain Du.
-You are here.

377
00:20:09,559 --> 00:20:10,200
They're inside.

378
00:20:11,240 --> 00:20:11,880
Hua.

379
00:20:12,079 --> 00:20:12,880
Dr. Sun went in too.

380
00:20:12,880 --> 00:20:14,240
Are you good today?

381
00:20:14,640 --> 00:20:15,599
They're doing a check.

382
00:20:19,079 --> 00:20:21,559
Tu Xiaohua, let's do a checkup.

383
00:20:21,839 --> 00:20:22,920
Who is she?

384
00:20:23,440 --> 00:20:24,440
Xiaohua's mother.

385
00:20:26,400 --> 00:20:27,000
Biological one.

386
00:20:27,440 --> 00:20:28,000
You found her?

387
00:20:28,279 --> 00:20:29,319
An illegal truck driver.

388
00:20:29,319 --> 00:20:30,160
A couple of days ago,

389
00:20:30,559 --> 00:20:32,720
the traffic police
caught illegal transporters.

390
00:20:33,119 --> 00:20:35,920
She rammed the checkpoint
and was detained and just released.

391
00:20:37,400 --> 00:20:38,640
Let's do a checkup.

392
00:20:39,039 --> 00:20:39,559
Don't move.

393
00:20:39,559 --> 00:20:40,640
No.

394
00:20:40,640 --> 00:20:41,920
Come on.

395
00:20:41,920 --> 00:20:44,279
- I am holding you.
- No.

396
00:20:44,640 --> 00:20:45,519
No.

397
00:20:45,519 --> 00:20:46,759
I am holding you.

398
00:20:49,799 --> 00:20:50,599
This way.

399
00:20:56,559 --> 00:20:58,759
Dr. Sun, how is she?

400
00:20:59,079 --> 00:21:00,559
She has severe PTSD.

401
00:21:01,160 --> 00:21:02,720
I don't recommend you go in now.

402
00:21:13,039 --> 00:21:14,720
Has the arrest request been approved?

403
00:21:15,359 --> 00:21:16,000
No.

404
00:21:17,039 --> 00:21:18,920
Only two days are left.

405
00:21:19,079 --> 00:21:20,240
We're running out of time.

406
00:21:20,240 --> 00:21:22,079
You're telling me now
that it's not approved?

407
00:21:22,079 --> 00:21:23,480
Should we pursue this case or not?

408
00:21:23,480 --> 00:21:24,160
Lower your voice.

409
00:21:33,720 --> 00:21:35,039
What's this? She just woke up.

410
00:21:35,039 --> 00:21:35,720
Let go.

411
00:21:35,920 --> 00:21:36,839
Calm down.

412
00:21:36,839 --> 00:21:38,319
I know what I'm doing.

413
00:21:38,799 --> 00:21:39,559
Let go.

414
00:21:42,640 --> 00:21:43,680
Hello, sorry to disturb.

415
00:21:45,359 --> 00:21:46,400
I'm a prosecutor.

416
00:21:47,839 --> 00:21:48,920
I'm a police officer.

417
00:21:50,200 --> 00:21:50,799
The thing is,

418
00:21:51,119 --> 00:21:52,559
we are very sorry,

419
00:21:52,559 --> 00:21:54,240
but we are running out of time.

420
00:21:55,200 --> 00:21:57,799
So I'd like to ask Xiaohua
a few questions.

421
00:21:57,799 --> 00:21:58,400
Is that okay?

422
00:22:02,039 --> 00:22:04,039
We really can't wait any longer.

423
00:22:06,079 --> 00:22:06,720
Hua,

424
00:22:08,720 --> 00:22:09,440
is it alright?

425
00:22:18,160 --> 00:22:18,880
Xiaohua,

426
00:22:19,680 --> 00:22:20,599
don't be afraid.

427
00:22:20,599 --> 00:22:21,759
I'm here to help you.

428
00:22:23,640 --> 00:22:24,799
I want to ask you something.

429
00:22:25,440 --> 00:22:27,319
That day, your dad took you and Xiaohu

430
00:22:27,319 --> 00:22:28,880
to the park together, right?

431
00:22:33,920 --> 00:22:35,880
Before you got on the boat,

432
00:22:35,880 --> 00:22:36,640
did you and Xiaohu

433
00:22:36,640 --> 00:22:37,839
both wear a jacket

434
00:22:37,839 --> 00:22:39,799
that could protect you?

435
00:22:44,119 --> 00:22:45,400
Here is my question.

436
00:22:46,039 --> 00:22:48,319
The safety buckles of the jackets

437
00:22:48,960 --> 00:22:50,160
were fastened.

438
00:22:50,279 --> 00:22:51,599
Why were they unfastened later?

439
00:23:01,839 --> 00:23:02,920
It's okay, Xiaohua.

440
00:23:03,480 --> 00:23:04,359
Take your time.

441
00:23:05,640 --> 00:23:07,119
They were fastened at first, right?

442
00:23:08,680 --> 00:23:09,720
Then they were unfastened.

443
00:23:09,720 --> 00:23:10,559
Why is that?

444
00:23:12,720 --> 00:23:14,039
I don't know why.

445
00:23:14,039 --> 00:23:15,240
Can you tell me?

446
00:23:35,880 --> 00:23:36,759
Do you still remember

447
00:23:36,759 --> 00:23:38,119
how you fell into the water?

448
00:23:39,119 --> 00:23:41,559
- Captain Du.
- I don't know. I don't know.

449
00:23:41,559 --> 00:23:42,680
Leave.

450
00:23:43,680 --> 00:23:44,400
I don't know.

451
00:23:44,400 --> 00:23:45,519
Leave. Now!

452
00:23:45,759 --> 00:23:47,119
I'm sorry.

453
00:23:47,640 --> 00:23:48,720
Let's go.

454
00:23:49,680 --> 00:23:50,839
I'm sorry.

455
00:23:52,640 --> 00:23:54,079
What were you doing?

456
00:23:54,079 --> 00:23:55,079
Why were you so hasty?

457
00:23:55,079 --> 00:23:56,440
I'm running out of time.

458
00:23:56,440 --> 00:23:57,920
I'm running out of time.

459
00:24:21,680 --> 00:24:23,000
What's the medicine you took?

460
00:24:23,880 --> 00:24:25,000
To treat irritability?

461
00:24:33,240 --> 00:24:34,400
I don't mind

462
00:24:34,400 --> 00:24:35,599
your bad attitude towards me.

463
00:24:36,039 --> 00:24:36,880
But when facing kids,

464
00:24:36,880 --> 00:24:37,880
we need to take it slow.

465
00:24:38,400 --> 00:24:40,440
Especially kids with such experiences.

466
00:24:41,039 --> 00:24:42,839
Fear can trigger stress responses.

467
00:24:44,240 --> 00:24:45,960
I don't want you in my car. Get off.

468
00:24:47,119 --> 00:24:51,119
Wait, how about
we analyze the situation again?

469
00:24:51,119 --> 00:24:52,680
Let's pool our ideas.

470
00:24:52,680 --> 00:24:54,599
I just feel that you are impatient

471
00:24:54,599 --> 00:24:55,599
with kids.

472
00:24:56,759 --> 00:24:57,839
Isn't our ultimate goal

473
00:24:57,839 --> 00:24:59,160
to protect the kids?

474
00:24:59,599 --> 00:25:02,200
You can't scare each kid
one by one, right?

475
00:25:02,200 --> 00:25:03,319
Move! The car ahead!

476
00:25:24,079 --> 00:25:25,079
Why are you back here?

477
00:25:25,200 --> 00:25:26,119
I'm working overtime.

478
00:25:26,119 --> 00:25:26,640
What?

479
00:25:26,640 --> 00:25:27,839
I need to work.

480
00:25:27,839 --> 00:25:28,920
You've been busy all day.

481
00:25:28,920 --> 00:25:30,000
Go back and rest.

482
00:25:30,000 --> 00:25:31,680
I don't have time to rest.

483
00:26:16,200 --> 00:26:16,920
Bai Enyu,

484
00:26:17,079 --> 00:26:18,440
are you cleaning the windows?

485
00:26:19,079 --> 00:26:19,680
Ma'am,

486
00:26:20,960 --> 00:26:21,960
you're still here?

487
00:26:22,079 --> 00:26:23,039
Come in quickly.

488
00:26:24,920 --> 00:26:25,640
Sit.

489
00:26:29,400 --> 00:26:31,119
You've done well these days.

490
00:26:32,200 --> 00:26:32,920
It's my job.

491
00:26:34,559 --> 00:26:36,400
You're not used to it, are you?

492
00:26:37,839 --> 00:26:38,880
Not really.

493
00:26:38,880 --> 00:26:41,880
It's just that compared to the work
at the Juvenile Correctional Facility,

494
00:26:42,720 --> 00:26:44,839
I've seen

495
00:26:46,119 --> 00:26:48,359
more heartbreaking things.

496
00:26:49,680 --> 00:26:52,799
I mean, with Prosecutor Lin.

497
00:26:59,920 --> 00:27:01,279
Do you have any conflicts?

498
00:27:02,440 --> 00:27:03,079
No.

499
00:27:03,319 --> 00:27:04,160
Not at all.

500
00:27:04,400 --> 00:27:05,559
Well,

501
00:27:06,920 --> 00:27:08,119
please don't misunderstand.

502
00:27:08,119 --> 00:27:10,599
I'm not here to tattle.

503
00:27:10,599 --> 00:27:12,680
I'm feeling very energetic right now.

504
00:27:12,680 --> 00:27:14,440
But I don't know how to use it.

505
00:27:14,440 --> 00:27:15,960
I want to share her burden of Xiaohua

506
00:27:16,880 --> 00:27:18,000
and Xiaohu's case.

507
00:27:18,359 --> 00:27:20,200
But I don't know how.

508
00:27:20,519 --> 00:27:23,119
It has only made things
more complicated.

509
00:27:23,480 --> 00:27:24,559
No need to overthink it.

510
00:27:24,559 --> 00:27:26,000
It has nothing to do with you.

511
00:27:27,039 --> 00:27:29,319
Let's give Prosecutor Lin some time.

512
00:27:31,720 --> 00:27:34,599
She went through
what those two kids went through.

513
00:27:38,200 --> 00:27:39,000
Is this the place?

514
00:27:43,440 --> 00:27:44,240
Hello.

515
00:27:46,400 --> 00:27:46,920
Hello.

516
00:27:47,119 --> 00:27:49,759
I'm a prosecutor
from the mobile procuratorate station

517
00:27:49,759 --> 00:27:51,480
of Linwan Village.

518
00:27:51,480 --> 00:27:52,640
My name is Zheng Yanlai.

519
00:27:54,480 --> 00:27:56,160
Are you Zhitao's mother?

520
00:27:56,400 --> 00:27:57,519
Yes, I am.

521
00:27:58,079 --> 00:27:59,039
And Mr. Lin...

522
00:27:59,599 --> 00:28:00,759
Mr. Lin is resting.

523
00:28:01,240 --> 00:28:02,839
Wait a moment. I'll go call him.

524
00:28:04,400 --> 00:28:06,079
Hurry. Someone
from the government is here.

525
00:28:06,799 --> 00:28:07,559
Get up.

526
00:28:07,960 --> 00:28:09,960
Mr. Lin,

527
00:28:11,136 --> 00:28:13,480
I'm a prosecutor from
the mobile procuratorate station

528
00:28:13,480 --> 00:28:15,039
of Linwan Village.

529
00:28:15,039 --> 00:28:15,960
I'm Zheng Yanlai.

530
00:28:16,680 --> 00:28:18,759
Your daughter reported some issues.

531
00:28:19,240 --> 00:28:20,839
If there are any problems,

532
00:28:21,319 --> 00:28:23,160
let's not resort to violence.

533
00:28:23,319 --> 00:28:25,000
Don't be violent with your wife either.

534
00:28:26,799 --> 00:28:27,360
Come here.

535
00:28:33,640 --> 00:28:35,000
Domestic violence is illegal.

536
00:28:35,000 --> 00:28:37,359
Can't you sit down
and talk calmly about whatever it is?

537
00:28:37,359 --> 00:28:38,680
Why must you resort to violence?

538
00:28:39,000 --> 00:28:39,880
They're my family.

539
00:28:39,880 --> 00:28:41,559
What does it have to do with you?

540
00:28:41,720 --> 00:28:43,079
If you keep doing this,

541
00:28:43,079 --> 00:28:44,559
I can report you to the police.

542
00:28:46,440 --> 00:28:47,240
What are you doing?

543
00:28:47,240 --> 00:28:47,799
Move!

544
00:28:48,039 --> 00:28:48,839
Move!

545
00:28:50,720 --> 00:28:51,279
You...

546
00:28:51,559 --> 00:28:52,400
Stop it.

547
00:28:52,680 --> 00:28:53,440
If you continue,

548
00:28:53,440 --> 00:28:54,912
I'll report it to the police.

549
00:28:55,079 --> 00:28:56,039
Let me go.

550
00:28:57,000 --> 00:28:59,039
Village Chief,
I didn't do anything wrong.

551
00:28:59,039 --> 00:29:00,359
Help, Village Chief.

552
00:29:00,359 --> 00:29:01,640
Disperse.

553
00:29:01,640 --> 00:29:02,680
