554
00:29:02,680 --> 00:29:05,039
How can his family live without him?

555
00:29:06,000 --> 00:29:07,079
You can't take him away.

556
00:29:07,079 --> 00:29:07,920
Tell the police

557
00:29:07,920 --> 00:29:08,839
he didn't hit you.

558
00:29:08,839 --> 00:29:10,200
You fell down by yourself.

559
00:29:10,359 --> 00:29:11,599
Her dad didn't hit her.

560
00:29:12,039 --> 00:29:12,920
He did nothing wrong.

561
00:29:12,920 --> 00:29:14,519
Why are you arresting him?

562
00:29:15,400 --> 00:29:16,200
Zhengfeng.

563
00:29:16,880 --> 00:29:17,799
Ma'am,

564
00:29:18,480 --> 00:29:19,599
please calm down.

565
00:29:20,720 --> 00:29:22,240
Can you help me?

566
00:29:22,519 --> 00:29:23,119
Help me.

567
00:29:23,119 --> 00:29:24,559
He can't go to jail.

568
00:29:24,755 --> 00:29:26,528
(Article about Little Tao's situation)

569
00:29:38,640 --> 00:29:39,279
Come in.

