since we already had kids,

680
00:35:15,199 --> 00:35:16,639
he would change

681
00:35:16,639 --> 00:35:17,800
and become better.

682
00:35:19,519 --> 00:35:20,280
However,

683
00:35:21,960 --> 00:35:23,000
nothing changed.

684
00:35:23,840 --> 00:35:25,480
I took care of everything inside

685
00:35:25,960 --> 00:35:26,880
and outside the house.

686
00:35:28,400 --> 00:35:31,480
Every day, he just asked me for money.

687
00:35:31,679 --> 00:35:33,039
I had no money for him.

688
00:35:33,039 --> 00:35:34,440
So he borrowed money from others

689
00:35:35,519 --> 00:35:36,880
and forced me to repay it for him.

690
00:35:37,239 --> 00:35:38,960
I really couldn't stand it anymore.

691
00:35:39,440 --> 00:35:40,840
So I separated from him.

692
00:35:40,840 --> 00:35:43,039
