694
00:35:44,679 --> 00:35:46,880
But he never gave me a single cent.

695
00:35:46,880 --> 00:35:47,639
I had no choice.

696
00:35:47,639 --> 00:35:48,840
I ran out of money.

697
00:35:49,400 --> 00:35:50,480
The kids grew older,

698
00:35:50,480 --> 00:35:51,760
